Name: begin
Description: The value for the MIB object is captured from the MIB when the Flow is first observed

Name: end
Description: The value for the MIB object is captured from the MIB when the Flow ends

Name: export
Description: The value for the MIB object is captured from the MIB at export time

Name: average
Description: The value for the MIB object is an average of multiple captures from the MIB over the observed life of the Flow
